Third-Party Attribution:

This project implements algorithms from the following research papers:

1. TurboQuant: Online Vector Quantization with Near-optimal Distortion Rate
   Copyright (c) 2025-2026 Google Research
   Authors: Amir Zandieh, Majid Daliri, Majid Hadian, Vahab Mirrokni
   License: Research and educational use permitted

2. QJL: 1-Bit Quantized JL Transform for KV Cache Quantization
   Copyright (c) 2024-2025 Google Research
   Authors: Amir Zandieh, Majid Daliri, Insu Han
   License: Research and educational use permitted

The implementation in this package is an independent work by Gaurav Chauhan,
based on the algorithms described in the above papers.
